metadata.name: The Legend of Zoeh
metadata.description: Once upon a time there was a forest full of magic. Zoeh lived in a small house. She used to play every day with her friends in the forest. Until one day the magic that kept the forest alive began to darken and her friends started to disappear. Zoeh's imagination was beginning to fade. There was only thing to do, so the little girl began a journey in search of a miracle to fix the forest
